<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ArmouryNet – Battalion Inventory Management System</title>
<style>
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:'Arial', sans-serif; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  body { color:#fff; overflow-x:hidden; background-color:#000; }

  /* Full page background - slightly dimmer */
  body::before {
    content:"";
    position:fixed;
    top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%;
    background: url('home2.webp') center/cover no-repeat fixed;
    background-size: cover;
    z-index:-1;
    filter: brightness(0.45); /* dimmed more for less visibility */
  }

  /* Header - almost fully transparent */
  header {
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    padding:6px 20px;
    background: rgba(20,20,20,0.005); /* ~99.5% transparent */
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: none; /* no visible border */
    position:relative; z-index:1;
  }

  header .logo-title { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; }
  header .logo-title img { height:65px; width:65px; object-fit:contain; }
  header .logo-title h1 { 
    font-size:2.1rem;
    font-family: 'GT America Extended', Arial, sans-serif; 
    font-weight: bold; 
    color: #fff; 
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; 
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  header nav a {
    margin-left:15px; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:8px;
    text-decoration:none; color:#fff; font-weight:bold; transition:0.3s ease;
  }
  header nav a:hover { color:#000; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); text-shadow: 0 0 8px #fff; }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
    display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; text-align:center;
    height:70vh; position:relative; z-index:1;
  }
  .hero-content { max-width:800px; }

  /* Main title slightly smaller & unbold */
  .hero-content h1 { font-size:2.23rem; margin-bottom:15px; font-weight: lighter; }

  /* Motto */
  .hero-content h3 {
    font-size:1.8rem;
    font-weight:bold;
    color:#fff;
    margin-bottom:12px;
  }

  /* Sub-motto */
  .hero-content p {
    font-size:1.2rem;
    color:#ccc;
    margin-bottom:30px;
  }

  /* Glass Button */
  .hero-content button {
    padding:15px 35px; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:bold;
    border:2px solid #fff; border-radius:12px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color:#fff;
    cursor:pointer; backdrop-filter: blur(8px); transition: 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px #fff, 0 0 10px #fff;
  }
  .hero-content button:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,1); color:#000;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px #fff, 0 0 30px #fff, 0 0 45px #fff;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  /* Features Section */
  .features {
    display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:space-around;
    gap:20px; padding:50px 20px; position: relative; z-index:1;
  }
  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-radius:20px; padding:30px; text-align:center; width:250px;
    box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition:0.3s;
  }
  .feature-card:hover { 
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px #fff, 0 0 30px #fff;
  }
  .feature-card h3 { margin-bottom:15px; color:#fff; }
  .feature-card p { font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.5; color:#ccc; }

  @media(max-width:900px){
    .features { flex-direction:column; align-items:center; }
    .hero-content h1 { font-size:2rem; }
    .hero-content h3 { font-size:1.6rem; }
    .hero-content p { font-size:1rem; }
  }
  
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo-title">
    <img src="logo.webp" alt="ArmouryNet Logo">
    <h1>ArmouryNet</h1>
  </div>
  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="/about">About</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Secure, Centralized, and Role-Based Management for Battalion Operations</h1>
    <h3>"वीर भोग्या वसुंधरा"</h3>
    <p>The Brave Shall Inherit the Earth</p>
    <a href="/login" class="hero-content-button-class"><button>Login</button></a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Personnel Management</h3>
    <p>Overview of soldier records, leave applications, and assignments.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Inventory Control</h3>
    <p>Manage weapons, ammo, rations, vehicles, and stock levels efficiently.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Reports & Alerts</h3>
    <p>Automated alerts, readiness reports, and real-time notifications.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Role-Based Access</h3>
    <p>CO, QM, Adjutant, MTO, Soldiers – all access controlled securely.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<script>
document.body.style.opacity = 0;
window.addEventListener("load", () => {
  document.body.style.transition = "opacity 1.2s ease-in-out";
  document.body.style.opacity = 1;
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
